A woke theatre company in Paris was dedicated to the notion that no human is illegal. However, it learned the hard way why people are not invited with open arms without a vetting process.

To signal their lack of virtue, theater managers at Gaîté Lyrique invited 200 migrants to a free show. However, they never left and the company has been forced to shut down since Dec.

title: Woke Theatre Company Invited 200 Migrants To A Free Show But They Refuse To Leave
